    "description": "<i><strong>你喜欢看成吨的单位为你服务吗？</strong></i><br><br><strong>涂鸦军队</strong> 是一款 <strong> 殖民地管理</strong> 游戏，你必须在其中探索洞穴。<br><br>只需点击几下即可收集资源。<br>使用你的资源制作单位，它们将帮助你收集、制作和战斗。<br>创建新建筑并升级它们以解锁新单位和新工艺。<br>为你的单位升级以提高生产力和功能。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134900/extras/da82be8563116998df0663442c12b2a9.poster.avif?t=1668504433\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134900/extras/da82be8563116998df0663442c12b2a9.webm?t=1668504433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134900/extras/da82be8563116998df0663442c12b2a9.mp4?t=1668504433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>如果你想进入下一个级别，请为 <strong> 战斗</strong> 做好准备。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134900/extras/a4f2eb7d6e0c8b12a3c3d29e187da6af.poster.avif?t=1668504433\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134900/extras/a4f2eb7d6e0c8b12a3c3d29e187da6af.webm?t=1668504433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134900/extras/a4f2eb7d6e0c8b12a3c3d29e187da6af.mp4?t=1668504433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你得知你童年的朋友在探索新洞穴时失踪了。<br>你的职责是进入这个巨大的地下并找到他！<br>如要找到他，你必须聪明、有条理且小心谨慎。 <strong>这个洞穴和其他洞穴不同......</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134900/extras/6851024b04566a67db6223144667753a.poster.avif?t=1668504433\" width=616 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134900/extras/6851024b04